Notes: Semifinals of the ECAC Upstate Championship
No. 1 seed Fisher advances to Sunday's championship game at 1 p.m. and will
play Union/UR winner -- career-high 27 points for Baum.  Union cut the lead
to six with two minutes left, but Fisher made its last 10 FTs to seal the win.
Game.Officials: Joe DeSain,  Rob Macomber,  John Proper
